reviews.text: It's a good place to chill but there is not much of small business, but instead a lot of big companies like tai hing and McDonald . But there are also a few affordable restaurant at ground floor , next to the computer shop .
Very clean surroundings you can play in playground all the time and do exercises.
No traditional Cantonese restaurant in the estate. Only some small scale fast food typed restaurants there.
A great housing estate with pretty gardens, nice security staff, decent shopping mall and fantastic access to all of HK via rail, bus, vehicle and walking.
I love it
